name: iShares 20+ Year U.S. Treasury Bond Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide income by replicating, to the extent possible, the performance of an index that is broadly representative of U.S. Treasury bonds with remaining maturities greater than 20 years, net of expenses. The ETF seeks to provide income by replicating, to the extent possible, the performance of an index that is broadly representative of U.S. Treasury bonds with remaining maturities greater than 20 years, net of expenses. The current index for the ETF is the ICE U.S. Treasury 20+ Year Bond Index.
